{"tid":2064532,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你香島中學真係痴撚線 以後唔好俾小朋友入去同班大陸人讀書","createTime":"2020-06-15T01:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T02:28:59.000Z","uid":208122,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dffe5dc6c5ef1c6eca47283102c4f1aca912f566","tid":2064532,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:28:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【香島老師要求廣東話上課被大陸家長投訴到解僱 學生：第一年入嚟讀已經後悔】</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n本月初九龍塘香島中學爆出政治審查老師，有任教藝術科的李老師，疑因容許學生於考試中演奏抗爭歌曲《願榮光歸香港》而被校方解僱。前日（6月12日）有學生發起九龍塘人鏈，支援被政治原因解僱的老師。<br />\n<br />\n本台訪問到香島中學學生，大爆除李老師之外，更有另一位本地體育老師因要求校內大陸學生課上使用廣東話溝通，而被大陸家長投訴，最後更被校方解僱。而學生更被迫購買《大公報》、《文匯報》等左報於早上閱讀。同學亦爆出這間傳統左派學校「校董會同副校都係共產黨人」，校方更排斥香港人，「當香港人係垃圾」，傾向收取大陸學生，班上40人只有5個香港學生，明言「第一年入嚟讀已經後悔」。<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nFacebook 專頁：中大校園電台 CUHK Campus Radio<br />\nYouTube 頻道：中大校園電台<br />\nInstagram: cuhk_campusradio<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cuhkcampusradio/videos/768078387062040/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcuhkcampusradio%2Fvideos%2F768078387062040%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8tg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=5d996cca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cuhkcampusradio/videos/768078387062040/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"cd824016cf89456272d56e00b042529a75c042c1","tid":2064532,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"改名做青島中學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b24098b01f267e0d6e45931c32ec147117c9b0","tid":2064532,"uid":118988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:34:34.000Z","msg":"香岛不嬲都左派架啦，今日先知咩？"},{"pid":"803dad4fd611e490d85ce80b69db243c29051dec","tid":2064532,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:00:05.000Z","msg":"呢間中學係67暴動有份整炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc05f64c96d250002035e9a67fc4205d24d6dc1","tid":2064532,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"803dad4fd611e490d85ce80b69db243c29051dec","tid":2064532,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:00:05.000Z","msg":"呢間中學係67暴動有份整炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:28:59.000Z","msg":"你大大聲講，佢地都分分鐘告唔入你誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}